show.description: Leena, working as the secretary to CEO Sameer under a secret identity, is deeply in love with him. When the company faces a cyber attack, she takes matters into her own hands, secretly handling the crisis. But her world shatters when she learns of Sameer’s engagement to Maya, leaving her torn and awestruck by the unexpected turn of events.
